    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When strange, uncanny looking forces start swarming Pale University, an arts student named Hue sets out to clean things up.... by making a mess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238010/extras/11a916746dd6384530cea6a1e7d20dde.avif?t=1770095170\" width=500 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art Attack is an action roguelike with a unique paint based combat system!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Hue, a student who loves their craft, and fights enemies using different paints, each with a different ability!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find items to upgrade your build!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and mix over 20 different colors of paint, each with unique properties!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a colorful cast of characters, with varied perspectives!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...And beat the crud out of of AI Generated monsters drawn by actual artists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238010/extras/bb27aa4f676e60dd5a9168906f4d6535.poster.avif?t=1770095170\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238010/extras/bb27aa4f676e60dd5a9168906f4d6535.webm?t=1770095170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238010/extras/bb27aa4f676e60dd5a9168906f4d6535.mp4?t=1770095170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
